	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106298009457885250">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.dbdebunk.com/page/page/603073.htm">DATABASE DEBUNKINGS - 2003 CONTENT</a>.&nbsp; There is some marvelous material in here.&nbsp;  Some of it is unnecessarily strident for my liking, and also a little too ad hominem.&nbsp;   I can understand the debate much easier without that.&nbsp;  And the errors seem to be clear as well.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106298009457885250">9/7/2003 05:14:54 PM</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
