	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106297934149127683">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.dbdebunk.com">DATABASE DEBUNKINGS - HOME</a>.&nbsp; this is a nice site managed by Fabian Pascal and Chris Date, apparently.&nbsp; One great value is their efforts to quote myths and bunk about relational databases and dispell the fallacies in them.&nbsp; I have been seeing some of that bunk in my class discussions, so I will happily refer people here.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297934149127683">9/7/2003 05:02:21 PM</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
