	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106297911074298860">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.pgro.uk7.net/ted_codd.htm">ted_codd</a>.&nbsp; This tribute by Chris Date provides valuable historical background on the evolution of Ted Codd's thinking and the establishment of the rubustness and enduring quality of the relational model for data bases.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297911074298860">9/7/2003 04:58:30 PM</a></span></div>
