	<a href="http://www.scism.sbu.ac.uk/~rmkemp/codd1979.pdf">[Codd1979]: Extending the Data Base Relational Model to Capture More Meaning - PDF</a>.&nbsp; Another key paper by Codd.  Again, this is a reference to the 38p. PDF file.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297640487666056">9/7/2003 04:13:24 PM</a></span></div>
