	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106297623309693470">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.scism.sbu.ac.uk/~rmkemp/codd1970.pdf">PDF: E. F. Codd Relational Model</a>.&nbsp; This link is to a PDF of the original 1970 paper.&nbsp; Don't go there unless you are ready for a lengthy download.&nbsp; Recommendation: Right-click on the link and do a Save Target As operation.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297623309693470">9/7/2003 04:10:33 PM</a></span></div>
