	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106297523314930886">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/c/Codd:E=_F=.html">DBLP: E. F. Codd</a>.&nbsp; What's nice about this bibliography is that you can see what Codd was doing before as well as during and after work on the relational model.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297523314930886">9/7/2003 03:53:53 PM</a></span></div>
