	<a href="http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/about/codd.html">Collected Works of E. F. Codd</a>.&nbsp; A nice bibliography that is compiled and maintained by ACM SigMOD.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297512887272614">9/7/2003 03:52:08 PM</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
