	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106297435963007095">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/journals/cacm/Codd70.html">Codd's "A Relational Model of Data for Large Shared Data Banks."  CACM 13(6): 377-387(1970)</a>.&nbsp; There is a PDF link but it doesn't seem to work.<br>
