	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106297412273365033">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.advogato.org/article/666.html">Edgar F. Codd, father of "relational database model" left us...</a>.&nbsp; A discussion around the report of Codd's death, identifying a key contribution: "The great contribution of master Codd besides the assertion that 'the entire information content of a relational database is represented in one and only one way: namely, as attribute values within tuples within relations' is his activism in promoting one theory of 'relational completeness of data base sublanguage'."<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297412273365033">9/7/2003 03:35:22 PM</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
