	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106297357749859508">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.bayarea.com/mld/mercurynews/news/5676110.htm">Mercury News | 04/20/2003 | Computer pioneer, dead at 79, revolutionized database system</a>.&nbsp; The obituary for E. F. Codd.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106297357749859508">9/7/2003 03:26:17 PM</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
