	<a name="106296157998094611">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.acm.org/sigmod/record/issues/0309/index.html">SIGMOD Record - web edition / September 2003</a>.&nbsp; This issue has a special section on Peer-to-Peer Data Management.&nbsp; I find that interesting because of the Feuding Lexicographers problem.&nbsp; Something to dig into a little more.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#106296157998094611">9/7/2003 12:06:19 PM</a></span></div>
<br>
