	<a href="http://www.acm.org/sigmod/record/issues/0109/">SIGMOD Record - web edition / September 2001</a>.&nbsp; The Guest Editor's message on XML and Heterogeneous data is being discussed in this weeks Web Applications seminar.&nbsp; I am out to discover what the difference is between heterogeneous and homogenous data, and whether what matters is simply that it is data.<br>
